which are conclusive evidence.

856
00:41:04,510 --> 00:41:05,360
Given your bond with your father,

857
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:07,290
I understand that you can't accept

858
00:41:07,470 --> 00:41:08,800
the reality right away.

859
00:41:10,430 --> 00:41:11,560
That's impossible.

860
00:41:12,680 --> 00:41:13,760
My father would never

861
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:15,090
collude with the enemy.

862
00:41:15,470 --> 00:41:16,280
Godfather,

863
00:41:16,990 --> 00:41:18,590
my father joined the military
when he was young.

864
00:41:18,590 --> 00:41:19,920
He has always zealously

865
00:41:19,950 --> 00:41:21,630
protected the country

866
00:41:21,680 --> 00:41:22,990
and the people.

867
00:41:23,030 --> 00:41:24,890
No matter what position he holds,

868
00:41:25,030 --> 00:41:26,840
his ambition has never changed.

869
00:41:45,430 --> 00:41:46,240
Now,

870
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:50,510
he is no longer in charge

871
00:41:50,510 --> 00:41:51,990
of Yangxi Prefecture.

872
00:41:54,630 --> 00:41:56,110
He asserts no influence

873
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:58,360
on the court's affairs.

874
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:03,550
I beg you, Godfather.

875
00:42:03,990 --> 00:42:05,650
Please save my father's life.

876
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:07,760
Ridiculous.

877
00:42:08,680 --> 00:42:10,610
Can you prove what you said is true?

878
00:42:11,470 --> 00:42:11,920
Do you know

879
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:13,840
the person plotting against your father

880
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:16,400
is actually your husband, Prince of Dingbei?

881
00:42:19,950 --> 00:42:21,110
It was he who offered to

882
00:42:21,110 --> 00:42:23,110
send a troop of Dingbei Army to

883
00:42:23,150 --> 00:42:24,400
escort your father back

884
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:25,880
from Lizhou.

885
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:28,360
Do you know what happened on the way?

886
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:30,150
A soldier from Dingbei Army

887
00:42:30,150 --> 00:42:31,950
released your father at night,

888
00:42:32,430 --> 00:42:34,550
insisting that it was the prince's order

889
00:42:34,550 --> 00:42:35,990
to set the marquis free.

890
00:42:36,240 --> 00:42:37,800
Doubtlessly, the prince did it

891
00:42:37,800 --> 00:42:39,070
only to prove

892
00:42:39,070 --> 00:42:40,280
your father guilty

893
00:42:40,310 --> 00:42:42,270
without implicating himself!

894
00:42:43,470 --> 00:42:44,530
That can't be true.

895
00:42:44,720 --> 00:42:46,360
Before your father was convicted,

896
00:42:46,360 --> 00:42:48,030
Prince of Dingbei led the Imperial Guards

897
00:42:48,030 --> 00:42:49,070
to confiscate his property.

898
00:42:49,070 --> 00:42:50,240
Why would he do that?

899
00:42:50,240 --> 00:42:51,950
He was apparently severing ties

900
00:42:51,950 --> 00:42:53,110
with your father.

901
00:42:54,320 --> 00:42:55,240
Tan’er,

902
00:42:55,840 --> 00:42:57,470
think about it.

903
00:42:57,550 --> 00:42:59,360
Since your father got in trouble,

904
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:01,080
what exactly has Jiang Xu done

905
00:43:01,110 --> 00:43:02,400
for the Ming family?

906
00:43:08,800 --> 00:43:09,590
Godfather,

907
00:43:10,200 --> 00:43:12,240
I don't care about political struggles,

908
00:43:12,240 --> 00:43:13,700
stances or conspiracies.

909
00:43:14,720 --> 00:43:16,920
Power, status and wealth

910
00:43:16,990 --> 00:43:18,510
mean nothing to me.

911
00:43:19,160 --> 00:43:21,090
All I ask is that my father can live.

912
00:43:31,360 --> 00:43:33,400
Marquis of Jing'an is an official.

913
00:43:33,470 --> 00:43:36,330
He is inevitably involved
in political struggles.

914
00:43:36,760 --> 00:43:39,530
He chose Prince
of Beiding to be your husband

915
00:43:39,590 --> 00:43:41,190
simply because the prince

916
00:43:41,210 --> 00:43:42,590
could bring more power

917
00:43:42,590 --> 00:43:44,680
to the Ming family. Don't you know?

